## RscEntry.content property

Contents of the entry.

**Signature:**

```typescript
content: Uint8Array;
```

## Remarks

This buffer may be a view on the buffer originally passed to [unpackRsc()](./rsc-tools.unpackrsc.md)<!-- -->. Modifying this buffer could modify the other buffer and vice versa.
